Config enable in your defconfig file:
-# CONFIG_IIO is not set
+CONFIG_IIO=y
+CONFIG_IIO_ST_ASM330LHHX=y
+CONFIG_IIO_ST_ASM330LHHX_I2C=y
+# CONFIG_IIO_ST_ASM330LHX_SPI is not set
+CONFIG_IIO_ST_ASM330LHHX_EN_BASIC_FEATURES=y
+CONFIG_IIO_ST_ASM330LHHX_MAY_WAKEUP=y
+# CONFIG_IIO_ST_ASM330LHHX_ASYNC_HW_TIMESTAMP is not set
+CONFIG_IIO_ST_ASM330LHHX_MLC_PRELOAD=y
+

Note:
1.You must disable some INPUT config in your defconfig file
# CONFIG_INPUT_ASM330LHH is not set
# CONFIG_INPUTASM330LHH_I2C is not set
# CONFIG_INPUT_ASM330LHH_IRQ_THREAD is not set
